news.title: Ramgarh limestone mine in Jaisalmer goes under hammer for 21% premium
news.para: The Ramgarh block fetched a premium of 21% over the offered price. Dalmiya Bhara Green Vision won the block in the auction.

news.title: Land acquisition completed on entire line except Godrej & Boyce plot: Maharashtra to HC
news.para: Of the total 508.17 km of rail track between Mumbai and Ahmedabad, about 21 km is to be underground. One of the entry points to the underground tunnel falls on the land at Vikhroli (owned by Godrej).

news.title: Bills to regularize illegal constructions in Kerala soon
news.para: As per the amendment proposed to the Kerala Panchayat Raj Act, 1994, and the Kerala Municipality Act, 1994, all the constructions that have been initiated or have been completed prior to November 7, 2019, can be regularized.
